Tennessee's waiting period law goes in mid-2015, and Podraza said he said he has been seen some women who wants to try to reverse a medical bortion that was already progressed. 其中一些妇女后来第二次改变了主意,接着堕胎,他作证. 这些逆转发生在尽管等待期.
